Class Customers

java.lang.Object
model.Customers
public class Customers extends Object
Customers Model class that handles the logic and attributes of a given Customer in the scheduler.

      Parameters:
      Customer_ID - = The ID of the given customer.
      Customer_Name - = The name of the given customer.
      Address - = The home address of the given customer.
      Postal_Code - = The postal code of the given customer.
      Phone - = The phone number of the given customer.
      Country_ID - = The ID of the Customer's given Country.
      Division_ID - = The ID of the given corresponding First-Level Division.
      Country - = The name of the given corresponding Country.
      Division - = The name of the given corresponding First-Level Division.
